{"tid":264601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九站擬允內地跨境執法    譚耀宗：你驚咪唔好坐高鐵囉","createTime":"2017-05-31T03:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T05:22:27.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d38a584c4d8cbaab8aa5d7e07797488146c626b8","tid":264601,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496196639_e0d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496196639_e0d7.png&h=547bba1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段原定明年第三季通車，但爭論多年的「一地兩檢」安排至今仍未落實。政府擬於西九總站劃出範圍，讓內地人員在港按內地法規，辦理海關及出入境程序，被質疑違反《基本法》，近月更先斬後奏，在站內興建內地口岸區。民建聯成員譚耀宗反斥，若部分人有意見，大可不坐高鐵，「你自己真係有問題，明顯想搞啲咩，或者你驚嘅時候，你咪唔好坐高鐵、唔返內地囉。普羅大眾大家守法，無任何問題」。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗早上在電台節目指，香港有見內地高鐵成功，主動要求連接，國家才配合。他承認若要在本港劃定內地執法區，內地和本港均要修訂法例，或額外授權，但他認為《基本法》並非一成不變，可按情況變化而調節或修改，「例如人大常委會要有決定，香港可能要修改法律」。他理解部分人對安排有疑問，但相信守法的普羅大眾不會覺得一地兩檢有問題，「到落實嘅時候，大家覺得無咩嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n人大委員長張德江早前在北京舉行的《基本法》實施20週年座談會上，宣稱中央對香港擁有全面管治權，及表明對「自決」、「港獨」不能視若無睹等。譚耀宗認為，張德江的講話非收緊對港管治，只重申中央立場，以及因應《基本法》實施以來的問題，講清楚《基本法》的原意，做好規範，防止《基本法》「走樣」。他又認為本港出現自決和「港獨」聲音，已觸動中央底線，令中央在很多問題上，要重申堅決落實一國兩制。"},{"pid":"1db186f324d84803ddb9b507f8fd67c9a5e8b123","tid":264601,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:15:03.000Z","msg":"咁一千億係咪除返730萬份, <br />\n<br />\n再回返水比我先？"},{"pid":"94c3fd8711b7bf228e2c2dc7583698165b020032","tid":264601,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"港共不意外"},{"pid":"2cafb07df5f5f5687378144a7f88230893e16181","tid":264601,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"咁應該所有犯法都係death penalty<br />\n唔犯法洗乜驚？"},{"pid":"d567c39e8194b158eb6454fb092e2b7b37c7a8ba","tid":264601,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"撚樣有樣睇"},{"pid":"f6f76c0edcb7797380b099ac66ced74d2412b5e8","tid":264601,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚樣有樣睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/e/e4/D8OH.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/640?cb=20110710112250\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fe4%2FD8OH.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F640%3Fcb%3D20110710112250&h=c197e66f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a21efe5aea419bf313c594ed182ff902c3890d70","tid":264601,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/e/e5/Di-LYK3.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/174?cb=20110710090751\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fe5%2FDi-LYK3.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F174%3Fcb%3D20110710090751&h=98864dea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52e93f02a815485338914911f22ef7d11e3d59df","tid":264601,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"689不允許人談港獨<br />\n驚你咪唔好傾港獨"},{"pid":"b4da9a363b9fa01929be260de7349f50b290ae61","tid":264601,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁一千億係咪除返730萬份, <br />\n<br />\n再回返水比我先？</blockquote><br />\n你回水俾我我以後唔搭又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae228c0ef1f65af2bd7315e650914a92e3817023","tid":264601,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"好快會變成你驚咪唔好出門口囉"},{"pid":"714b22a9dd73a9799e7bcb9684120bf6c928576d","tid":264601,"uid":635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"依家又同你講基本法唔係一成不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n說好的五十年不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c658fa46d3cc7f3d873638a9d6fae39f67d4d84f","tid":264601,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"原來溫水煮蛙真係咁有用<br />\n住下住下都可以係香港中間既位置執法<br />\n下一步就唔小心出左閘拉人<br />\n跟住又人大釋法<br />\n最後成街公安"},{"pid":"022ca2c9916308156361342ced8fef4bb84ab2bc","tid":264601,"uid":6639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">譚耀宗早上在電台節目指，香港有見內地高鐵成功，主動要求連接，國家才配合。<br />\n</span><br />\n調返轉黎講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}